regulating_news.description:
Does the submission explicitly comment on whether professional news content should be excluded or included under the proposed changes? We are only interested specifically in professional news content. Do not infer whether this is commented on or base your response on implications from other comments, we are only interested in express and direct comments on the exclusion of professional news content. If no comment on this issue, return an empty object or nothing at all. If the submission does discuss this issue, return which of the following categories best describes the submission’s position. Possible positions:1. Professional news content should be excluded
2. Professional news content should be included
3. Other (please describe in one sentence or less). For the most correct option, please also provide a detailed explanation as to why the submission holds that particular view, extracting the relevant comments from the submission. Your response should be in valid JSON format as so: {'position': 'one of the possible outlined positions', 'description': 'Detailed description'}

For example, if a submission claims professional news content should be excluded, you would respond:

{'position': 'Professional news content should be excluded', 'description': 'Detailed explanation why here'}

republished_news.description:
Does the submission explicitly comment on whether content published by news media organisations be excluded when republished on other platforms? Do not infer whether this is commented on or base your response on implications from other comments, we are only interested in express and direct comments on the exclusion of republished news content. If the submission does discuss this issue, return which of the following categories best describes the submission’s position. Possible positions:
1. Republished professional news content should be excluded
2. Republished professional news content should be included
3. Other (please describe in one sentence or less). For the most correct option, please also provide a detailed explanation as to why the submission holds that particular view, ensuring that you extract the relevant comments from the submission. Your response should be in valid JSON format as so: {'position': 'one of the possible outlined positions', 'description': 'Detailed description'}

For example, if a submission claims republished professional news content should be included, you would respond:

{'position': 'Republished professional news content should be included', 'description': 'Detailed explanation why here'}
